[arquitetura dos modulos/libs]
Podem ser 3rd party: modules, libs e services. controllers e jobs isolados nao.
Módulo: user
modules/
    user/
        autoload.php ou user.php
        controllers/
            UserController.php
        services/
            UserService.php
        database/
            user.yml
Service: 
zapi
google-captcha